---
const sizes = "(min-width: 1024px) 28rem, 22rem"; // lg:w-[28rem], base:w-[22rem]
---
<section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Two-tone background -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-20 grid grid-cols-12">
    <div class="col-span-5 bg-black"></div>
    <div class="col-span-7 bg-[#FBF7F4]"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container relative grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
    <!-- Stacked frames + image (left) -->
    <div class="md:col-span-5 relative">
      <!-- back black block -->
      <div class="absolute -left-16 -top-24 w-[26rem] h-[28rem] bg-black rounded-2xl -z-10"></div>
      <!-- thin "gold" frame -->
      <div class="absolute -left-6 top-10 w-[24rem] h-[22rem] rounded-xl border border-[#B8A27A] bg-transparent -z-10"></div>

      <!-- main image card -->
      <div class="relative inline-block">
        <picture>
          <source type="image/webp" srcset="/split-portrait-640.webp 640w, /split-portrait-960.webp 960w, /split-portrait-1200.webp 1200w" sizes={sizes} />
          <img
            src="/split-portrait-960.jpg"
            alt="D‑Essence Wellness treatment room"
            class="block w-[22rem] lg:w-[28rem] h-auto rounded-md shadow-xl ring-1 ring-black/10 object-cover object-center"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Editorial text (right) -->
    <div class="md:col-span-7">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <div class="text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-black/60">MED SPA IN NEW WINDSOR</div>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase">Being Real Looks<br/>And Feels Great</h2>

        <p class="mt-6 text-[15px] leading-7 text-black/80">
          Has anyone told you lately that you’re beautiful? You are! At Hudson Valley Beauty Lab & Medi Spa, we see it.
          And if your goal is to accentuate your natural features for a personal look that’s amazing, HVBL is your luxurious home for skin‑focused, authentic results.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-7 text-black/80">
          We offer 100% nonsurgical, minimally‑invasive treatments such as injectables, advanced skin care services, laser resurfacing and the latest in microblading techniques.
          We specialize in full face rejuvenation, regenerative medicine and emphasize the need to treat the face as a whole.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] leading-7 text-black/80">
          We’ve recently relocated our business to the Newburgh Riverfront. As we settle into our new location you will see continued updates and changes to our website, further introducing you to our new space!
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
